{"tid":1843153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋全部都係殺人兇手","createTime":"2020-01-26T05:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T05:49:22.000Z","uid":200545,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3c24d678de541ef6e55ead8aa55a9bba932f93be","tid":1843153,"uid":200545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:36:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係講緊唔肯擺工嘅你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n唔單止係醫護行業<br />\n<br />\n政府到呢一刻仲唔封關<br />\n香港人真係要自救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔理你藍黃定港豬都好<br />\n呢刻真係要醒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個關一日唔封<br />\n一日都會有中招嘅人偷入黎香港<br />\n<br />\n去到醫院政府就推啲醫護去死<br />\n有乜用姐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要醫好嘅機率極低<br />\n更何況源頭一直都冇減少<br />\n唔好以為自己生死簽抽得後就唔關你事<br />\n好大機會輪到你都有得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前最緊要就係全民罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其是醫護行業<br />\n要最短時間內令政府跪低封關<br />\n咁先可以減少係香港擴散嘅風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將人命生命傷亡減到最低<br />\n<br />\n政府就係睇死你地班大愛撚唔敢罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以推你地去做擋箭牌<br />\n所以我地要話比政府聽<br />\n醫護唔係condom!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會陪你打一場睇唔到盡頭嘅仗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但如果你最後一刻都冇罷工嘅話<br />\n請記住你雙手係沾滿鮮血<br />\n你都係一個不折不扣嘅殺人兇手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 家族入面全部醫護都講好左會罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係醫護嘅你<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">願唔願意同佢哋一齊罷工呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"46e194dde7f0045496d44483c649d5393a7309db","tid":1843153,"uid":90328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:36:43.000Z","msg":"我願意同醫護一齊罷工"},{"pid":"a150d571a015d066c679afe02962a065a59caa1e","tid":1843153,"uid":200545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:37:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先減少源頭 後治療病患</span></span>"},{"pid":"b2b2a6d96e0caac3697f1460477bf8a211926e6c","tid":1843153,"uid":34676,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾標題，拉"},{"pid":"66e1f0f2385c9feb1e8c1569b4b79fb6f9c2a550","tid":1843153,"uid":132322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:37:53.000Z","msg":"我願意同醫護一齊罷工"},{"pid":"a9b625558df11c1f3488f767e1cfd764eaa88263","tid":1843153,"uid":200545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人要身體健康啊！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9d77df279b51664864067d906296579ccd8f44ce","tid":1843153,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:38:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ce0d0a3355bfd714a1514656d86aeb23b27a301a","tid":1843153,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔死多d點攬炒點爭取五大訴求"},{"pid":"8f151a041559fdcb5abaa9188ac713bf32b424c6","tid":1843153,"uid":200545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2b2a6d96e0caac3697f1460477bf8a211926e6c","tid":1843153,"uid":34676,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾標題，拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:38:55.000Z","msg":"係咪講中你唔罷工啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949b4e178766b51ce1254cac2b424b752a549139","tid":1843153,"uid":211364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:39:07.000Z","msg":"一齊罷"},{"pid":"6cf21e922aefe48caf473a